Package: SmoothImage
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Norm Matloff <normmatloff@gmail.com> [cre,aut], 
   Jessica Tsoi <jessicattsoi@gmail.com> [aut]
Maintainer: Norm Matloff <normmatloff@gmail.com>
Title: Image Smoothing Via Regression Modeling
Description: Use of regression models to ameliorate imperfections in color images.
             Option to choose percentage of original image to retain. Usage of k-NN
             with default at 1 and option to increase k. 
Depends: stats,utils,pixmap
Suggests: 
ByteCompile: yes
NeedsCompilation: no
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/matloff/SmoothImage
BugReports: https://github.com/matloff/SmoothImage/issues
